{"ts":"2026-07-19T03:43:08.238Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"append","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/body","value":"GH-609. settings.json + schema/{types,statuses,fields,workflows}.json are single git-tracked JSON files with no merge driver; conflicting edits leave conflict markers → invalid JSON → pm silently falls back to defaults and validate reports ok:true, so governance settings/custom schema are silently lost behind a green gate. Same masking class as pm-cxyv at the config layer. Fix direction: config-integrity validate check (parse failure = hard fail) + key-level JSON merge guidance/driver."},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-19T03:43:08.238Z"}],"before_hash":"820c2646bbd3cee2ce2f5f98474452868f1f2ce625c60ef1ee75c2a960421aa3","after_hash":"e91e0380b80ecadcf95509d40748c9d3bd801038d765ed80fbd3a1a512875d42"}
